==About==
===Format===
''*Registrations: March 14th - 21st, 2026
* '''IN-Game Qualifiers:''''' Mar 27th - 29th, 2026
* '''Round 1:''''' Apr 3rd - 6th, 2026
** 512 Teams, 4 matchdays.
** Teams divided into 32 groups with 16 Teams in each group.
** Each team plays a total of 6 matches.<!--
